item.title: japanese cheese cake
item.description:
japanese cheese cake

hellooo

i made the famous instagram reel “japanese” cheese cake which is really just greek yogurt and biscotti.

sooo i made it into tirimisu version with my decaf espresso!! and i drank with my little matcha latte yaaaaaaah
